
Dependencies:

 * libattr1
 * libblkid
 * libuuid
 * libscrypt
 * libsodium
 * libkeyutils
 * liburcu
 * pkg-config
 * zlib1g

On debian, you can install these with
    apt install -y pkg-config libblkid-dev uuid-dev libscrypt-dev libsodium-dev
	libkeyutils-dev liburcu-dev zlib1g-dev libattr1-dev

Then, just make && make install
